Feature: Users
  In order to administrate the users
  As an admin
  I want to see them
  
  Scenario: Administrate users
    Given a logged in user
    When I go to the user page
    Then I should see "Administrate users"
    And I should see "Usergroups"
    
  Scenario: Add new user
    Given a logged in user
    When I go to the new user page
    Then I should see "Add user"
    And I should see "Username"
    And I should see "E-Mail"
    And I should see "Password"
    And I should see "Confirm password"